{"tid":2301213,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支那護士誤將墮胎藥當安胎藥　準媽媽食後洗胃不果憂後遺症無奈墮胎","createTime":"2020-11-26T06:30:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T11:28:11.000Z","uid":130626,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5dfb76ff01f1b1fbe63158b61131fa15961c6c11","tid":2301213,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T06:30:11.000Z","msg":"內地發生一宗嚴重醫療事故。一名懷孕16周的準媽媽本來想到醫院安胎，但護士將安胎藥發錯成墮胎藥。準媽媽食了3粒墮胎藥後才被告訴「食錯藥了」。雖然院方馬上進行催吐、洗胃等措施挽救，但準媽媽仍擔心嬰兒有後遺症，無奈中止懷孕。<br />\n<br />\n綜合內媒報道，安徽一名懷孕16周的孕婦於11月4日由丈夫施先生陪同，住進醫院安胎。11月6日早上6點半左右，護士像往常一樣幫孕婦量體溫，並拿藥給她食。但事後，護士突然告訴夫婦「食錯藥了」。<br />\n<br />\n原來，護士將墮胎藥「米非司酮」誤當是安胎藥，並讓孕婦誤服3粒。院方隨即幫孕婦催吐、稀釋等措施，但效果不明顯，於是再去另一間醫院洗胃，但結果不理想。<br />\n<br />\n施先生指，妻子因事故精神上受到刺激，雖然超聲波檢查顯示胎兒情況良好，但實在擔心胎兒會因誤食藥物而有後遺症，希望中止懷孕。<br />\n<br />\n院方：落胎及安胎患者住同一間病房<br />\n院方就醫護人員的失誤深表遺憾，並解釋由於住院患者較多，床位緊張，醫護人員安排落胎及安胎的患者住進同一間病房，導致事故發生。<br />\n<br />\n目前，涉事護士已停職。院方與患者家屬經調解後達成一致，醫院向家屬賠償9萬多元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n醫生：「米非司酮」對孕婦屬禁用藥物<br />\n山東大學附屬生殖醫院泌尿外科和男性生殖科醫生許超在微博表示，「米非司酮」是一種類固醇類抗孕激素製劑，在妊娠期的安全評級是X級，屬於絕對禁用的藥物，不能服用。<br />\n<br />\n雖然事後有催吐、洗胃，超聲波檢查顯示胎兒狀態良好，但藥物對胎兒有沒有影響，影響有多大是無法保證的。所以家屬希望中止懷孕，也能理解。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2810000/2812980/baby_thumb_20201126_ch_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2810000%2F2812980%2Fbaby_thumb_20201126_ch_1024.jpg&h=1999025e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b8a95564ae3f42650d7823e02f41250d3092fda","tid":2301213,"uid":177089,"like":27,"dislike":3,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T06:32:53.000Z","msg":"支那幼蝗-1 公德無量"},{"pid":"62d005cc77a6a709a0ce59c9f563e29831a12aad","tid":2301213,"uid":39710,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T06:33:41.000Z","msg":"係咪驗到係女呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4197b10049304b9849fbc2d9ae7ade33b72a3255","tid":2301213,"uid":126283,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T06:33:49.000Z","msg":"遲下如果引入支那醫護<br />\n有排俾廢老受<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4104848252df2ab1e04b3b62e831f41c90eebe3","tid":2301213,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T06:34:33.000Z","msg":"孩子的父親是。。。"},{"pid":"7133c1535ebcc489d42d7d053a2989f5a00ae6c0","tid":2301213,"uid":118120,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T06:35:31.000Z","msg":"冇俾紅包就求其做野<br />\n有俾紅包保證樣樣做足唔會出錯"},{"pid":"2630a55f00101d3434cf290baefa7518de4221fe","tid":2301213,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T06:36:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73d3be4ec6cc6682681384628c367edb70d9a075","tid":2301213,"uid":295459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62d005cc77a6a709a0ce59c9f563e29831a12aad","tid":2301213,"uid":39710,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T06:33:41.000Z","msg":"係咪驗到係女呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T06:37:15.000Z","msg":"肯肯定係<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25eb28a185bd0f861c03b063d129d2beec5c7bce","tid"